"Floresta !Floresta" translates to "Forest !Forest" in English and to "Forest or not Forest" in coding. The title reflects the battle between technological advances and Nature, inviting one to think about the future of our natural resources. In that sense, a forest of computer-generated trees illustrates this cover.

